text: Woh Ku-inak: ku-baxi Muusa yaabukeek gamadal sandugut kaa hayisaay, niil weeqaytut kaa ruubaay, tokkel Niil weeqayti isik qaxal kaa ayyaaqe-le, tokkel yok qaduwwiiy kaak qaduwwih yan num kaa beele iyyaanamah maysaxxaageh tet niysixxige, kaadu Muusaw yok yan kacanu kol qide koo ablinnaanih mari koo yakcineeh yi-dacayrih gubat qartaah tanbemkeh iyye Yalli
